Subject: Request for MIME media type Application/Vendor Tree - vnd.cybank

Name : Helmee

E-mail : helmee&my.cybank.net

MIME media type name : Application

MIME subtype name : Vendor Tree - vnd.cybank

Required parameters : none

Optional parameters : 
none

Encoding considerations : 
Cybank is in 8bit binary and requires encoding when sent over transport
incapble of transferring binary data.

Security considerations : 
Cybank uses RSA1024 public key encryption for key exchange, and block
chaining triple DES, plus a tamperproof key lock for transmission of
encrypted data.  The Cybank packet also contains E-Commerce
informations which is useful to the system. No currently defined Cybank
packet has any "executable" material.

Interoperability considerations : 


Published specification : 
The specifications for this content-type are proprietary. They are
specified by Cybank. The registration of this content-type is intended
only to provide a convention for labeling this proprietary data type
within the MIME/HTTP environment and does not specify any details about
the content format or semantics, except to refer to the software and
specifications provided by Cybank.
